  <description><![CDATA[<p>Formerly an Alpine barn, Hotel La Chance has been painstakingly renovated into a delightful boutique hotel. Using local materials combined with modern Italian flair, the hotel strikes the perfect balance between authentic Alpine charm and contemporary design. Just a short walk from the lifts, guests can even ski back to the hotel conditions permitting. Wellness area with whirlpool, sauna and steam room is on hand to aid relaxation (free before 4pm).</p>]]></description>
